According to the analysis of mathematical theory, there is a peak rice yield of model (3) at a particular fertilization rate, corresponding to the fertilization rate that gave the maximum yield. Therefore, according to the principle of calculus, we can order the derivative of rice yield Y with respect to N, P and K in model (3) to be zero and can obtain the formula for the fertilization rate for the maximum yield:4\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
