Model (3) is a nonlinear model that cannot be directly linearized, so the model parameters are estimated by the use of a nonlinear least squares method27. If the nonlinear fertilizer response model is Y = f (X, a), the nonlinear least squares problem can be solved to obtain an estimated value of the parameter a:6\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
